(6, 5, 'Inspiring Scene From The Movie â€œRocky Balboaâ€', 'http://www.mairovergara.com/aprendendo-ingles-com-videos-005-inspiring-scene-from-the-movie-rocky-balboa/', 'https://youtu.be/0dKmgPMDnCI', 'Inspiring Scene From The Movie â€œRocky Balboaâ€\r\n\r\nRobert: This is only gonna end up bad for you, and itâ€™s gonna end up bad for me.\r\n\r\nRocky: You think Iâ€™m hurting you?\r\n\r\nRobert: Yeah in a way you are.\r\n\r\nRocky: Thatâ€™s the last thing I ever want to do.\r\n\r\nRobert: I know thatâ€™s not what you want to do, but thatâ€™s just the way that it is. Donâ€™t you care what people think? Doesnâ€™t it bother you that people are making you out to be a joke, and that I might be included in that? Do you think thatâ€™s right? Do you?\r\n\r\nRocky: You ainâ€™t gonna believe this, but you used to fit right here. Iâ€™d hold you up and say to your mother, â€œthis kidâ€™s gonna be the best kid in the world\". This kidâ€™s gonna be somebody better than anybody I ever knew, and you grew up good and wonderful. It was great just watching. Every day was like a privilege. Then the time come for you to be your own man, and take on the world and you did. But somewhere along the line, you changed. You stopped being you. You let people stick their finger in your face, and tell you youâ€™re no good, and when things got hard, you started looking for something to blame, like a big shadow. Let me tell you something you already know. The world ainâ€™t all sunshine and rainbows. Itâ€™s a very mean and nasty place, and I donâ€™t care how tough you are, it will beat you to your knees, and keep you there permanently if you let it. You, me, or nobody is gonna hit as hard as life, but it ainâ€™t about how hard youâ€™re hit. Itâ€™s about how hard you can get hit and keep moving forward. How much you can take and keep moving forward!, Thatâ€™s how winning is done!, Now if you know what youâ€™re worth, then go out and get your worth, but you gotta be willing to take the hits, and not 